00:56:40,579 --> 00:56:42,739
[SPEAKER_01] tako da nemam problem prič ljudima.

709
00:56:42,739 --> 00:56:43,780
[SPEAKER_01] I onda kažem, ono, proste,

710
00:56:43,780 --> 00:56:45,320
[SPEAKER_01] molim, dođite probati moj proizvod.

711
00:56:45,320 --> 00:56:45,619
[SPEAKER_01] Da.

712
00:56:45,619 --> 00:56:46,460
[SPEAKER_01] Baš proizvod.

713
00:56:46,460 --> 00:56:47,320
[SPEAKER_01] Pa di mi, to radite.

714
00:56:47,320 --> 00:56:47,760
[SPEAKER_01] Znaš?

715
00:56:47,760 --> 00:56:49,179
[SPEAKER_01] I onda kad ljudima kažeš,

716
00:56:49,179 --> 00:56:51,639
[SPEAKER_01] znači, imaš kupca, ono, for life.

717
00:56:51,639 --> 00:56:53,880
[SPEAKER_01] Znaš, for life, pogotovo ako mu se svidi.

718
00:56:54,000 --> 00:56:54,739
[SPEAKER_01] Ako mu se ne svidi,

719
00:56:54,739 --> 00:56:56,300
[SPEAKER_01] opet će suportirati i podržati,

720
00:56:56,300 --> 00:56:56,860
[SPEAKER_01] jer je naša.

721
00:56:56,860 --> 00:56:58,960
[SPEAKER_01] Tako je, imao je neko dobro iskustvo

722
00:56:58,960 --> 00:57:00,340
[SPEAKER_01] na kraju ko vidi vlasnicu,

723
00:57:00,340 --> 00:57:01,219
[SPEAKER_02] stvarno, ovo,

724
00:57:01,219 --> 00:57:03,059
[SPEAKER_02] i za proizvoda koja stoji tamo

725
00:57:03,059 --> 00:57:03,920
[SPEAKER_02] i distribuira ga.

726
00:57:03,920 --> 00:57:05,400
[SPEAKER_02] Pa je, za to mi kažu da sam luda,

727
00:57:05,400 --> 00:57:06,480
[SPEAKER_02] kao, zašto ti to radiš?

728
00:57:06,480 --> 00:57:08,000
[SPEAKER_02] Ja se kažem, ba, zašto ne, kao?

729
00:57:08,000 --> 00:57:10,760
[SPEAKER_02] Samo ti ostani luda, molim te,

730
00:57:10,760 --> 00:57:12,079
[SPEAKER_02] nemoj nikad doći u normalu,

731
00:57:12,079 --> 00:57:13,000
[SPEAKER_02] jer onda gubimo,

732
00:57:13,000 --> 00:57:14,599
[SPEAKER_02] znaš, ovaj neki kreativni,

733
00:57:14,599 --> 00:57:15,480
[SPEAKER_02] tvoj izričaj.

734
00:57:15,719 --> 00:57:18,099
[SPEAKER_02] Što bih htjela zapravo,

735
00:57:18,099 --> 00:57:20,159
[SPEAKER_02] evo, kako se sad bližimo kraju,

736
00:57:20,159 --> 00:57:21,960
[SPEAKER_02] znam da možda,

737
00:57:21,960 --> 00:57:23,760
[SPEAKER_02] dragi gledatelji, slušatelji,

738
00:57:23,760 --> 00:57:24,559
[SPEAKER_02] slušateljice,

739
00:57:24,559 --> 00:57:25,920
[SPEAKER_02] bih htjeli da ovi razgovori

740
00:57:25,920 --> 00:57:26,679
[SPEAKER_02] dulja traju,

741
00:57:26,679 --> 00:57:28,019
[SPEAKER_02] ali zato uvijek možemo

742
00:57:28,019 --> 00:57:29,760
[SPEAKER_02] Maju pozvati ponovo u goste,

743
00:57:29,760 --> 00:57:31,280
[SPEAKER_02] nakon možda godinu dana,

744
00:57:31,280 --> 00:57:32,360
[SPEAKER_02] da vidimo kako ide.

745
00:57:32,360 --> 00:57:33,519
[SPEAKER_02] Ili šu je kluda.

746
00:57:33,519 --> 00:57:34,760
[SPEAKER_02] Ili šu je kluda,

747
00:57:34,760 --> 00:57:35,780
[SPEAKER_02] ili šu je kreativna,

748
00:57:35,780 --> 00:57:36,900
[SPEAKER_02] ali evo za kraj,

749
00:57:36,900 --> 00:57:38,980
[SPEAKER_02] budući da nam se kraj bliži,

750
00:57:38,980 --> 00:57:40,420
[SPEAKER_02] koje bi bile glavne poruke,

751
00:57:40,420 --> 00:57:40,920
[SPEAKER_02] recimo,

752
00:57:42,139 --> 00:57:43,559
[SPEAKER_02] koje bi bilo glavno učenje,

753
00:57:43,559 --> 00:57:44,880
[SPEAKER_02] kad pričaš već o primjeru

754
00:57:44,880 --> 00:57:45,719
[SPEAKER_02] dobre prakse,

755
00:57:45,719 --> 00:57:47,039
[SPEAKER_02] što bih htjela podijeliti

756
00:57:47,039 --> 00:57:48,619
[SPEAKER_02] s ljudima koji se susreću

757
00:57:48,619 --> 00:57:49,280
[SPEAKER_02] sa stresom,

758
00:57:49,280 --> 00:57:50,679
[SPEAKER_02] što god to stres za njih bio,

759
00:57:50,679 --> 00:57:52,019
[SPEAKER_02] da li neka bolest,

760
00:57:52,019 --> 00:57:53,860
[SPEAKER_02] ili neka teška životna situacija,

761
00:57:53,860 --> 00:57:55,239
[SPEAKER_02] ili možda neki neprekidni

762
00:57:55,239 --> 00:57:56,960
[SPEAKER_02] niz malih stresnih stvari,

763
00:57:56,960 --> 00:57:58,340
[SPEAKER_02] koje nam nekad znaju

764
00:57:58,340 --> 00:57:59,320
[SPEAKER_02] posisa živce,

765
00:57:59,320 --> 00:58:00,539
[SPEAKER_02] da nismo toga ni svjesni.

766
00:58:00,539 --> 00:58:02,980
[SPEAKER_02] Što bih rekla ovako za kraj?

767
00:58:02,980 --> 00:58:05,239
[SPEAKER_01] Pa, mislim da ne bi trebali

768
00:58:05,239 --> 00:58:06,679
[SPEAKER_01] pocijnjivati pomoć drugoga,

769
00:58:06,679 --> 00:58:07,940
[SPEAKER_01] jednostavno tražiti pomoć.

770
00:58:08,659 --> 00:58:11,139
[SPEAKER_01] Stvarno mislim da je to jako hrabro

771
00:58:11,139 --> 00:58:13,659
[SPEAKER_01] za moliti nekoga kada si loše

772
00:58:13,659 --> 00:58:14,440
[SPEAKER_01] da ti pomogne,

773
00:58:14,440 --> 00:58:16,420
[SPEAKER_01] da bude tu i da se sluša,

774
00:58:16,420 --> 00:58:17,940
[SPEAKER_01] meni je to svakako pomoglo

775
00:58:17,940 --> 00:58:20,340
[SPEAKER_01] i to ne znači da si slaba osoba,

776
00:58:20,340 --> 00:58:21,159
[SPEAKER_01] da si slabić,

777
00:58:21,159 --> 00:58:22,860
[SPEAKER_01] to samo znači da daješ sve od sebe,

778
00:58:22,860 --> 00:58:23,780
[SPEAKER_01] da ti budeš dobro

779
00:58:23,780 --> 00:58:25,559
[SPEAKER_01] i da se, ono, boriš se za sebe

780
00:58:25,559 --> 00:58:27,099
[SPEAKER_01] i ta jedna dosljednost,

781
00:58:27,099 --> 00:58:28,679
[SPEAKER_01] baš je dosljednost bitna,

782
00:58:28,679 --> 00:58:29,480
[SPEAKER_01] to sam naučila

783
00:58:29,480 --> 00:58:31,360
[SPEAKER_01] i ono, nemojte odustati od sebe,

784
00:58:31,360 --> 00:58:31,820
[SPEAKER_01] nikad,

785
00:58:31,820 --> 00:58:33,440
[SPEAKER_01] jer ono, baš smo svi posebni

786
00:58:33,440 --> 00:58:34,480
[SPEAKER_01] takvi kakvi jesmo.

787
00:58:34,480 --> 00:58:37,059
[SPEAKER_02] Krasno, Majo.

788
00:58:37,559 --> 00:58:38,760
[SPEAKER_02] Znači, traži pomoć,

789
00:58:38,760 --> 00:58:42,099
[SPEAKER_02] budi dosljedna

790
00:58:42,099 --> 00:58:43,820
[SPEAKER_02] i ostani luda.

791
00:58:43,820 --> 00:58:44,079
[SPEAKER_02] Da.

792
00:58:44,079 --> 00:58:45,179
[SPEAKER_02] Za lud.

793
00:58:45,179 --> 00:58:45,900
[SPEAKER_02] Za lud.

794
00:58:45,900 --> 00:58:47,539
[SPEAKER_02] Predivno.

795
00:58:47,539 --> 00:58:48,900
[SPEAKER_02] Za kraj, hvala ti puno

796
00:58:48,900 --> 00:58:50,019
[SPEAKER_02] na ovom razgovoru

797
00:58:50,019 --> 00:58:51,480
[SPEAKER_02] i sretno s Baricama.

798
00:58:51,480 --> 00:58:52,579
[SPEAKER_02] Ja znam da sam,

799
00:58:52,579 --> 00:58:54,300
[SPEAKER_02] evo, tvoj kupac za život.

800
00:58:54,300 --> 00:58:55,119
[SPEAKER_02] Hvala ti puno.

801
00:58:55,119 --> 00:58:55,900
[SPEAKER_02] Hvala te, Vijana.

802
00:58:55,900 --> 00:58:56,579
[SPEAKER_02] Bilo je divno.

